(
<figureCitation id="13472A73FFA64407D3DCF8DDFF2DF8C3" box="[160,241,1836,1863]" captionStart="FIGURES 9–15" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1909,1933]" captionTargetBox="[209,1371,192,1872]" captionTargetId="figure-17@5.[201,1386,181,1885]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 9–15. 9. HOLOTYPE ♀ Mimonephelotes enganensis Breuning, 1970, habitus (photo: G. Chemin); 10. ditto, lateral view (photo: G. Chemin); 11. ditto, labels (photo: G. Chemin); 12. HT ♀ Anhammus luzonicus Breuning, 1982, habitus (photo: G. Chemin); 13. ditto, lateral view (photo: G. Chemin); 14. ditto, labels (photographed by: G. Chemin); 15. ♂ Nephelotus enganensis, habitus (Photo: G. Chemin)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577769" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6577769/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="83">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
